subtitle: who would you reach out to in love that
you work so hard to build a wall to keep
away if you had one more week in this
waking dream what would you be grateful
for what would you see as a gift that
you once feared or detested would you
see a handicap as a stepping stone or
Catalyst for change all of these things
you experience now will change and
vanish no one knows the moment of the
grand shift but the mighty Elder of
light and the higher Realms of creative
power where God covets all life
